ster nearly struck after the seventh sprint when he crashed with 24 laps to go after a touch of wheels out of turn two.\", \"from\": 1694, \"to\": 1913, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Frenchman\", \"from\": 1694, \"to\": 1707}, {\"ngram\": \"the Omnium overall standings\", \"from\": 1732, \"to\": 1760}, {\"ngram\": \"the sixth lap\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 1780}, {\"ngram\": \"disaster\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1798}, {\"ngram\": \"the seventh sprint\", \"from\": 1819, \"to\": 1837}, {\"ngram\": \"24 laps\", \"from\": 1859, \"to\": 1866}, {\"ngram\": \"a touch\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 1886}, {\"ngram\": \"wheels\", \"from\": 1890, \"to\": 1896}, {\"ngram\": \"turn\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 1908}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was quickly up and back in the race and even going on the attack, taking out sprint nine and then stealing away with Leitao and Alberto Torres (Spain) to seal the gold medal.\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 2091, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2045, \"end\": 2052, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alberto_Giacometti\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5449263861585596e-14, \"text\": \"Alberto\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alberto_Giacometti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alberto_Giacometti\"}, {\"begin\": 2061, \"end\": 2066, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999655042308, \"rank\": 3.449472783721922e-08, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 1944, \"to\": 1952}, {\"ngram\": \"the attack\", \"from\": 1971, \"to\": 1981}, {\"ngram\": \"sprint\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2000}, {\"ngram\": \"Leitao\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2040}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold medal\", \"from\": 2076, \"to\": 2090}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It could have sent any other rider into panic stations, but Thomas stayed calm, got back into the race before the next sprint, and was able to parlay his advantage into victory.\", \"from\": 2093, \"to\": 2270, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2153, \"end\": 2159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"score\": 0.8780562708367359, \"rank\": 0.13887680710214756, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any other rider\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2127}, {\"ngram\": \"panic stations\", \"from\": 2133, \"to\": 2147}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2195}, {\"ngram\": \"the next sprint\", \"from\": 2203, \"to\": 2218}, {\"ngram\": \"his advantage\", \"from\": 2243, \"to\": 2256}, {\"ngram\": \"victory\", \"from\": 2262, \"to\": 2269}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When you are in the middle of an effort and you fall, the first thing you need to do is stand up and look at your bike.\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2392, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the middle\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2299}, {\"ngram\": \"an effort\", \"from\": 2303, \"to\": 2312}, {\"ngram\": \"the first thing\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2342}, {\"ngram\": \"your bike\", \"from\": 2382, \"to\": 2391}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think I changed bikes - I moved around a little to see if I'd broken anything and everything was fine.\", \"from\": 2393, \"to\": 2497, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bikes\", \"from\": 2411, \"to\": 2416}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2464, \"to\": 2472}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2477, \"to\": 2487}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I just started again because I knew I'd done a good race.\", \"from\": 2498, \"to\": 2555, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a good race\", \"from\": 2543, \"to\": 2554}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I wasn't penalized, I just kept cool and after the sprint, I showed I was still there.\", \"from\": 2556, \"to\": 2642, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sprint\", \"from\": 2603, \"to\": 2613}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So this fall was just a joke.\\\"\", \"from\": 2643, \"to\": 2673, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this fall\", \"from\": 2646, \"to\": 2655}, {\"ngram\": \"just a joke\", \"from\": 2660, \"to\": 2671}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The latest race content, interviews, features, reviews and expert buying guides, direct to your inbox!\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2777, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The latest race content\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2698}, {\"ngram\": \"interviews\", \"from\": 2700, \"to\": 2710}, {\"ngram\": \"features\", \"from\": 2712, \"to\": 2720}, {\"ngram\": \"reviews\", \"from\": 2722, \"to\": 2729}, {\"ngram\": \"expert buying guides\", \"from\": 2734, \"to\": 2754}, {\"ngram\": \"your inbox\", \"from\": 2766, \"to\": 2776}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Leitao, who stunned the world when he soloed away repeatedly during the races in the Omnium world championships in Glasgow last year, wasn't given as much leeway at the Olympics but still showed immense poise and intelligence in fighting for the silver medal.\", \"from\": 2779, \"to\": 3038, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2864, \"end\": 2870, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omnium\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.217350955266739e-51, \"text\": \"Omnium\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omnium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omnium\"}, {\"begin\": 2894, \"end\": 2901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"score\": 0.9898460349977675, \"rank\": 0.010258125650074184, \"text\": \"Glasgow\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\"}], \"noun_ph