u get into a race like this and you put it all together, you get, in this case, a silver medal.\\\"\", \"from\": 3396, \"to\": 3499, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a race\", \"from\": 3414, \"to\": 3420}, {\"ngram\": \"this case\", \"from\": 3472, \"to\": 3481}, {\"ngram\": \"a silver medal\", \"from\": 3483, \"to\": 3497}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Leitao had a strong tempo race and finished seventh in the scratch race, but there was a confusing incident during the elimination race where the officials apparently did not ring the bell before calling him out of the race in the next lap.\", \"from\": 3501, \"to\": 3741, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Leitao\", \"from\": 3501, \"to\": 3507}, {\"ngram\": \"a strong tempo race\", \"from\": 3512, \"to\": 3531}, {\"ngram\": \"the scratch race\", \"from\": 3556, \"to\": 3572}, {\"ngram\": \"a confusing incident\", \"from\": 3588, \"to\": 3608}, {\"ngram\": \"the elimination race\", \"from\": 3616, \"to\": 3636}, {\"ngram\": \"the officials\", \"from\": 3643, \"to\": 3656}, {\"ngram\": \"the bell\", \"from\": 3681, \"to\": 3689}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 3716, \"to\": 3724}, {\"ngram\": \"the next lap\", \"from\": 3728, \"to\": 3740}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I will not say it's not my fault, I did not hear the bell, many people did not hear the bell - I will have to check it after but after it's done, you can not do anything to change it.\", \"from\": 3743, \"to\": 3927, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my fault\", \"from\": 3768, \"to\": 3776}, {\"ngram\": \"the bell\", \"from\": 3793, \"to\": 3801}, {\"ngram\": \"many people\", \"from\": 3803, \"to\": 3814}, {\"ngram\": \"the bell\", \"from\": 3828, \"to\": 3836}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 3905, \"to\": 3913}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You have to keep going and do your best in the next race.\", \"from\": 3928, \"to\": 3985, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the next race\", \"from\": 3971, \"to\": 3984}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think it's not my fault.\\\"\", \"from\": 3986, \"to\": 4013, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my fault\", \"from\": 4003, \"to\": 4011}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, he came out hitting in the points race, one of five riders to lap the field twice, which helped him move ahead of Van Den Bossche, who could only lap once.\", \"from\": 4015, \"to\": 4176, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the points race\", \"from\": 4044, \"to\": 4059}, {\"ngram\": \"five riders\", \"from\": 4068, \"to\": 4079}, {\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 4087, \"to\": 4096}, {\"ngram\": \"Van Den Bossche\", \"from\": 4135, \"to\": 4150}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The emotions are always there and the rivals are so good you cannot believe too early, you have to keep fighting.\", \"from\": 4178, \"to\": 4292, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The emotions\", \"from\": 4179, \"to\": 4191}, {\"ngram\": \"the rivals\", \"from\": 4213, \"to\": 4223}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When I crossed the line and I saw I did it, it was super nice.\", \"from\": 4293, \"to\": 4355, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 4308, \"to\": 4316}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's unbelievable to achieve it,\\\" Leitao said.\", \"from\": 4356, \"to\": 4402, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Leitao\", \"from\": 4390, \"to\": 4396}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van Den Bossche raced aggressively in the early races.\", \"from\": 4404, \"to\": 4458, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Van Den Bossche\", \"from\": 4404, \"to\": 4419}, {\"ngram\": \"the early races\", \"from\": 4442, \"to\": 4457}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Of course, I was third in the Scratch, won the Tempo race, and did a decent Elimination, so you feel the momentum and you know that it's the day that it can happen.\", \"from\": 4460, \"to\": 4625, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4491, \"end\": 4498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glossary_of_North_American_horse_racing\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.805021534796436e-25, \"text\": \"Scratch\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glossary_of_North_American_horse_racing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glossary_of_North_American_horse_racing\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Tempo race\", \"from\": 4504, \"to\": 4518}, {\"ngram\": \"a decent Elimination\", \"from\": 4528, \"to\": 4548}, {\"ngram\": \"the momentum\", \"from\": 4562, \"to\": 4574}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 4598, \"to\": 4605}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You have to stay cool.\", \"from\": 4626, \"to\": 4648, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I pressed my gut, and tried to do that as much as possible.\", \"from\": 4649, \"to\": 4708, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my gut\", \"from\": 4659, \"to\": 4665}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I made some mistakes in the end, focusing too much on the medal.\", \"from\": 4709, \"to\": 4773, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some mistakes\", \"from\": 4716, \"to\": 4729}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 4733, \"to\": 4740}, {\"ngram\": \"the medal\", \"from\": 4763, \"to\": 4772}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was not perfect, but that does not matter, the result is what counts.\\\"\", \"from\": 4774, \"to\": 4847, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the result\", \"from\": 4820, \"to\": 4830}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's been really emotional to me as well.\", \"from\": 4849, \"to\": 4891, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is one of the highest things to reach in my career and to do it at this age (23) already, that's something.\\\"\", \"from\": 4892, \"to\": 5005, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the highest things\", \"from\": 4907, \"to\": 4925}, {\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 4938, \"to\": 4947}, {\"ngram\": \"this age\", \"from\": 4964, \"to\": 4972}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 4994, \"to\": 5003}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Benjamin Thomas of France thrilled his home country's Olympic velodrome, lapping the field with three other riders to take the first race in the men's Omnium on Thursday at theParis Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 5007, \"to\": 5203, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5007, \"end\": 5022, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin_Thomas_(cyclist)\", \"score\": 0.7746466892492642, \"rank\": 0.23636363636346383, \"text\": \"Benjamin Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin_Thomas_(cyclist)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin_Thomas_(cyclist)\"}, {\"begin\": 5026, \"end\": 5032, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999374341092369, \"rank\": 5.1869641158082946e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his home country's Olympic velodrome\", \"from\": 5042, \"to\": 5078}, {\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 5088, \"to\": 5097}, {\"ngram\": \"three other riders\", \"from\": 5103, \"to\": 5121}, {\"ngram\": \"the first race\", \"from\": 5130, \"to\": 5144}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's Omnium\", \"from\": 5148, \"to\": 5164}, {\"ngram\": \"Thursday\", \"from\": 5168, \"to\": 5176}, {\"ngram\": \"theParis Olympic Games\", \"from\": 5180, \"to\": 5202}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thomas finished ahead of breakaway companions Niklas Larsen (Denmark) and Fabio Van Den Bossche (Belgium) to take the lead in the four-race event, with the Netherlands Jan-Willem van Schip finishing fourth out of the move that lapped the field.\", \"from\": 5205, \"to\": 5449, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5205, \"end\": 5211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"score\": 0.8780562708367359,